title: GetPrevModule (Function)
text:
FUNCTION GetPrevModule :
IModule
Returns the previous module in depth-first preorder of the module tree.
Returns 0 if (and only if) itfM is the first module in the preorder of the tree.

rows.Name: itfM
rows.Comment:
The module instance that is queried for the previous
instance  (must not be 0)
